Thankfully it’s not equipped with a video screen, else your charade would be broken immediately. You clear your throat, lowering your voice a few pitches to imitate one of the pigs. “Yes sir. She put up a fight.”

The voice on the other end cackles. “Ha! Good work! Show those federal fucks what they get. Gotta pay Bozch for the tip…” The link cuts, and you let out a sigh of relief.

